{"type": "article", "id": 30598, "title": "全包式扶手椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-04T22:58:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160804182515i1tIBV2KCLnu4YQs.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>想要在开放式的工作环境中创造一个私密空间？一张能把你包裹住的椅子或许是个不错的主意。这张名为 Ara 的扶手椅是 <a href=\"http://www.perezochando.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">perezochando</a> 专门为西班牙家具品牌 <a href=\"http://www.missana.es/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Missana</a> 所设计的，高大的椅背是它的一大特色，就像是屏风一样包裹在座椅周围，在一定程度上可以减少外界的干扰。Ara 的一根金属椅腿上还额外设计了一张小木桌，供人们摆放物品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804182528bzd1N9UEKYW8I3G4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804182529WJG6oc50jnOfiXbd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.678484\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804182529YQ4RGBi5mrPMVXh1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497555\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}